GraphViz-DBI-General version 0.1
=================================

GraphViz::DBI::General is an object-oriented module that provides 
the capability to automatically graphs of database schemas 
(i.e. foreign key connections between tables).

This is a subclass of GraphViz::DBI. It is intended to work 
in the general case, and has been tested with PostgreSQL.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  GraphViz
  GraphViz::DBI
  DBI

